Incoming messages are sorted within the Message Index under the following categories: All Messages, Loyalty, Fleet, Mission, Resource, Manufacturing, Defense, Conflict, Chat, and Advice. R2-D2 will notify you each time a new message is received; the appropriate icon will also highlight in the Message Alert bar that runs down the left side of the Command Center.  Note that the icons in the Message Alert bar match the tabs in the Message Index.  Press F6 to access the Message Index from the Command Center; alternately, you can click on the appropriate Message Alert icon to view messages of a specific type.